com.atlassian.jira.issue.search.parameters.lucene.PermissionsParameter builds the Lucene query that ensure security permissions are respect during searches.

It would appear that it doesnt take to much effort to build a "smart" query when Issue Level Security Schemes are used.  



Users have report that this makes searching very slow.  This needs further verification to ensure that the building of a smarter query will actually translate into a faster search/display time.

